[
  {
    "text": "Matthew chapter eight",
    "start": 3.04,
    "end": 4.0
  },
  {
    "text": "verse eighteen is",
    "start": 4.0,
    "end": 5.59
  },
  {
    "text": "where you want to be.",
    "start": 5.59,
    "end": 6.47
  },
  {
    "text": "When Jesus saw the crowd around him,",
    "start": 9.03,
    "end": 11.27
  },
  {
    "text": "he gave orders to cross to the other side of the lake.",
    "start": 12.099999,
    "end": 14.74
  },
  {
    "text": "Then a teacher of the law came to him and said,",
    "start": 15.81,
    "end": 18.130001
  },
  {
    "text": "teacher,",
    "start": 18.130001,
    "end": 18.69
  },
  {
    "text": "I will follow you wherever you go.",
    "start": 18.69,
    "end": 20.87
  },
  {
    "text": "Jesus replied,",
    "start": 21.89,
    "end": 22.93
  },
  {
    "text": "foxes have holes and",
    "start": 23.96,
    "end": 25.32
  },
  {
    "text": "birds of the air have nests.",
    "start": 25.32,
    "end": 26.84
  },
  {
    "text": "But the son of man has no place to lay his head.",
    "start": 27.66,
    "end": 30.14
  },
  {
    "text": "Another disciple said to him,",
    "start": 31.16,
    "end": 32.84
  },
  {
    "text": "Lord,",
    "start": 32.84,
    "end": 33.24
  },
  {
    "text": "first let me go and bury my father.",
    "start": 33.44,
    "end": 35.6
  },
  {
    "text": "But Jesus told him,",
    "start": 36.94,
    "end": 38.22
  },
  {
    "text": "follow me.",
    "start": 38.22,
    "end": 38.86
  },
  {
    "text": "And let the dead bury their own dead.",
    "start": 40.05,
    "end": 41.89
  },
  {
    "text": "Then he got into a boat,",
    "start": 43.36,
    "end": 44.8
  },
  {
    "text": "and his disciples followed him.",
    "start": 44.88,
    "end": 46.16
  },
  {
    "text": "Without warning,",
    "start": 46.81,
    "end": 47.690002
  },
  {
    "text": "a furious storm came up on the lake",
    "start": 47.690002,
    "end": 49.850002
  },
  {
    "text": "so that the waves swept over the boat.",
    "start": 50.01,
    "end": 52.17
  },
  {
    "text": "But Jesus was sleeping.",
    "start": 53.16,
    "end": 55.0
  },
  {
    "text": "The disciples went and woke him saying,",
    "start": 56.100002,
    "end": 58.18
  },
  {
    "text": "Lord,",
    "start": 58.18,
    "end": 58.5
  },
  {
    "text": "save us.",
    "start": 59.030003,
    "end": 59.670002
  },
  {
    "text": "We're going to drown.",
    "start": 59.670002,
    "end": 60.55
  },
  {
    "text": "He replied,",
    "start": 61.66,
    "end": 62.379997
  },
  {
    "text": "you of little faith,",
    "start": 63.66,
    "end": 64.94
  },
  {
    "text": "why are you so afraid?",
    "start": 66.07,
    "end": 67.27
  },
  {
    "text": "And then he got up",
    "start": 68.25,
    "end": 69.05
  },
  {
    "text": "and rebuked the winds and the waves",
    "start": 69.05,
    "end": 71.29
  },
  {
    "text": "and it was completely calm.",
    "start": 71.57,
    "end": 73.329994
  },
  {
    "text": "The men were amazed and asked,",
    "start": 74.54,
    "end": 76.700005
  },
  {
    "text": "what kind of man is this?",
    "start": 77.54,
    "end": 78.979996
  },
  {
    "text": "Even the winds and the waves obey him.",
    "start": 79.85,
    "end": 82.009995
  },
  {
    "text": "When he arrived at the other side in the region of the Gadarenes,",
    "start": 83.32,
    "end": 86.520004
  },
  {
    "text": "two demon possessed men coming",
    "start": 87.200005,
    "end": 89.36
  },
  {
    "text": "from the tombs met him.",
    "start": 89.36,
    "end": 90.48
  },
  {
    "text": "They were so violent that no one could pass that way.",
    "start": 91.21,
    "end": 94.73
  },
  {
    "text": "We we do in many ways,",
    "start": 1528.0,
    "end": 1529.93
  },
  {
    "text": "but there are ways in which we don't feel it too.",
    "start": 1529.93,
    "end": 1532.13
  },
  {
    "text": "Our sickness,",
    "start": 1533.89,
    "end": 1534.6099997
  },
  {
    "text": "the evil in this world,",
    "start": 1535.9300003,
    "end": 1537.29
  },
  {
    "text": "the the hardships,",
    "start": 1537.29,
    "end": 1539.2699995
  },
  {
    "text": "the impact of the shame and guilt of our sin.",
    "start": 1539.2699995,
    "end": 1541.349999
  },
  {
    "text": "We don't always feel or experience the power and goodness of Jesus to us in our lives.",
    "start": 1541.79,
    "end": 1546.740002
  },
  {
    "text": "Not like they do in this story anyway.",
    "start": 1547.31,
    "end": 1549.31
  },
  {
    "text": "So it is different.",
    "start": 1549.31,
    "end": 1549.949999
  },
  {
    "text": "Because our hope is ultimately the day when Jesus returns to right",
    "start": 1552.22,
    "end": 1557.77
  },
  {
    "text": "all that's wrong.",
    "start": 1557.77,
    "end": 1558.73
  },
  {
    "text": "And yet, it's also different for us too",
    "start": 1560.89,
    "end": 1565.7
  },
  {
    "text": "because we're this side of the cross.",
    "start": 1566.51,
    "end": 1568.43
  },
  {
    "text": "Not that side like them.",
    "start": 1569.719997,
    "end": 1571.0
  },
  {
    "text": "We're the side where where where all of Matthew's gospel",
    "start": 1571.850002,
    "end": 1575.13
  },
  {
    "text": "is heading to",
    "start": 1575.13,
    "end": 1575.690002
  },
  {
    "text": "is to is where it's building.",
    "start": 1575.690002,
    "end": 1577.15
  },
  {
    "text": "We're past the moment where Jesus dies and rises again.",
    "start": 1578.22,
    "end": 1581.82
  },
  {
    "text": "Such that we might not feel his goodness at points in our life,",
    "start": 1583.81,
    "end": 1587.43
  },
  {
    "text": "but we can look back",
    "start": 1588.14,
    "end": 1589.34
  },
  {
    "text": "and see it to us.",
    "start": 1589.34,
    "end": 1590.86
  },
  {
    "text": "Full ball turned up to eleven.",
    "start": 1591.11,
    "end": 1592.63
  },
  {
    "text": "As we behold the death and the resurrection of Jesus,",
    "start": 1593.409996,
    "end": 1597.33
  },
  {
    "text": "we're assured of his power and his goodness for us.",
    "start": 1598.22,
    "end": 1600.78
  },
  {
    "text": "Of forgiveness,",
    "start": 1601.299995,
    "end": 1602.18
  },
  {
    "text": "of an end to evil,",
    "start": 1602.18,
    "end": 1602.979996
  },
  {
    "text": "of an end to suffering when he returns,",
    "start": 1602.979996,
    "end": 1604.82
  },
  {
    "text": "all assured because he died and rose again.",
    "start": 1605.45,
    "end": 1607.53
  },
  {
    "text": "You see how that hems us in?",
    "start": 1609.44,
    "end": 1611.12
  },
  {
    "text": "And it holds us there no matter our experience in life.",
    "start": 1612.299995,
    "end": 1616.14
  },
  {
    "text": "The the cross,",
    "start": 1616.14,
    "end": 1617.32
  },
  {
    "text": "the empty tomb,",
    "start": 1617.32,
    "end": 1618.12
  },
  {
    "text": "the risen Jesus,",
    "start": 1618.12,
    "end": 1618.920006
  },
  {
    "text": "It's where we fully see the power and goodness of him.",
    "start": 1619.59,
    "end": 1623.74
  },
  {
    "text": "Enough that you can trust him?",
    "start": 1625.73,
    "end": 1627.81
  },
  {
    "text": "Whatever your experience in life may be.",
    "start": 1628.96,
    "end": 1630.96
  },
  {
    "text": "In fact,",
    "start": 1634.27,
    "end": 1634.75
  },
  {
    "text": "more than that,",
    "start": 1636.06,
    "end": 1636.7
  },
  {
    "text": "It's where we see the power and the goodness of Jesus enough that we can actually follow him?",
    "start": 1638.85,
    "end": 1647.15
  },
  {
    "text": "This is key.",
    "start": 1648.7,
    "end": 1649.42
  },
  {
    "text": "Because this is what this is what Jesus' power",
    "start": 1651.43,
    "end": 1653.909996
  },
  {
    "text": "and his goodness demands.",
    "start": 1653.909996,
    "end": 1656.06999
  },
  {
    "text": "It demands we follow him.",
    "start": 1657.56,
    "end": 1660.12999
  },
  {
    "text": "Now one of my favorite things to do here in Newcastle in summer is to go for a swim in in Merriweather Baths.",
    "start": 1662.03,
    "end": 1669.42
  },
  {
    "text": "It gets harder to do around this time of year.",
    "start": 1669.91,
    "end": 1672.07
  },
  {
    "text": "It gets a bit cold,",
    "start": 1672.07,
    "end": 1673.03
  },
  {
    "text": "and I'm getting a little bit soft in my old age,",
    "start": 1673.03,
    "end": 1675.09001
  },
  {
    "text": "though.",
    "start": 1675.09001,
    "end": 1675.25
  },
  {
    "text": "Last year,",
    "start": 1675.87,
    "end": 1676.75
  },
  {
    "text": "a friend of mine here from church,",
    "start": 1676.90999,
    "end": 1678.59
  },
  {
    "text": "a friend of mine,",
    "start": 1678.59,
    "end": 1679.15
  },
  {
    "text": "we would try and go swimming during the winter",
    "start": 1679.15,
    "end": 1681.8
  },
  {
    "text": "for ten minutes,",
    "start": 1682.21,
    "end": 1683.09001
  },
  {
    "text": "at least ten minutes once or twice a week.",
    "start": 1683.09001,
    "end": 1685.17001
  },
  {
    "text": "We try and stay in the water.",
    "start": 1685.17001,
    "end": 1686.13
  },
  {
    "text": "And when you're in the water,",
    "start": 1687.03,
    "end": 1689.08
  },
  {
    "text": "it's actually not that bad.",
    "start": 1689.08,
    "end": 1690.12
  },
  {
    "text": "The worst part of the process is trying to transition from being outside the water into the water.",
    "start": 1691.1,
    "end": 1697.6100000000001
  },
  {
    "text": "That's the hardest part,",
    "start": 1697.6100000000001,
    "end": 1698.97
  },
  {
    "text": "especially if you try to ease in slowly.",
    "start": 1698.97,
    "end": 1700.98999
  },
  {
    "text": "You kinda got halfway in,",
    "start": 1700.98999,
    "end": 1702.1100000000001
  },
  {
    "text": "and you, like, had to back out",
    "start": 1702.1100000000001,
    "end": 1703.06999
  },
  {
    "text": "and the best thing to do was just to commit.",
    "start": 1703.06999,
    "end": 1707.18001
  },
  {
    "text": "And launch yourself not hold back,",
    "start": 1707.92,
    "end": 1711.05
  },
  {
    "text": "go for it,",
    "start": 1711.05,
    "end": 1711.77
  },
  {
    "text": "go all in with everything.",
    "start": 1711.77,
    "end": 1714.48999
  },
  {
    "text": "And that's what Jesus' power",
    "start": 1716.54,
    "end": 1717.9
  },
  {
    "text": "and goodness demands of us.",
    "start": 1717.9,
    "end": 1719.42
  },
  {
    "text": "That we go all in with everything,",
    "start": 1721.1100000000001,
    "end": 1723.72
  },
  {
    "text": "In fact,",
    "start": 1725.62001,
    "end": 1726.18001
  },
  {
    "text": "this is the point Jesus himself makes right back at the start of this passage.",
    "start": 1726.18001,
    "end": 1730.78
  },
  {
    "text": "Just come back with me to chapter eight verse eighteen.",
    "start": 1732.2,
    "end": 1734.92
  },
  {
    "text": "Where we meet these two guys who who wanna follow Jesus,",
    "start": 1735.6100000000001,
    "end": 1739.13
  },
  {
    "text": "but have a look at how Jesus responds to them there.",
    "start": 1739.95,
    "end": 1742.19
  },
  {
    "text": "Verse eighteen,",
    "start": 1743.87001,
    "end": 1744.59
  },
  {
    "text": "it says,",
    "start": 1744.59,
    "end": 1744.91
  },
  {
    "text": "when Jesus saw the crowd around him,",
    "start": 1745.67001,
    "end": 1747.91
  },
  {
    "text": "he gave orders",
    "start": 1748.52,
    "end": 1749.56
  },
  {
    "text": "to cross to the other side of the lake.",
    "start": 1749.56,
    "end": 1751.16
  },
  {
    "text": "Then a teacher of the law came to him and said,",
    "start": 1752.07,
    "end": 1754.23001
  },
  {
    "text": "teacher,",
    "start": 1754.56,
    "end": 1755.3600000000001
  },
  {
    "text": "I will follow you wherever you go.",
    "start": 1755.3600000000001,
    "end": 1757.52
  },
  {
    "text": "Jesus replied,",
    "start": 1758.82,
    "end": 1760.1
  },
  {
    "text": "foxes have dens",
    "start": 1760.1,
    "end": 1761.22
  },
  {
    "text": "and birds have nests",
    "start": 1761.22,
    "end": 1762.74
  },
  {
    "text": "but the son of man has no place to lay his head.",
    "start": 1763.29001,
    "end": 1765.77
  },
  {
    "text": "Another disciple said to him,",
    "start": 1766.98,
    "end": 1768.58
  },
  {
    "text": "Lord,",
    "start": 1768.58,
    "end": 1768.82
  },
  {
    "text": "first let me go and bury my father.",
    "start": 1769.20001,
    "end": 1771.28001
  },
  {
    "text": "But Jesus told him,",
    "start": 1771.28001,
    "end": 1772.0
  },
  {
    "text": "follow me and let the dead bury their own dead.",
    "start": 1772.1,
    "end": 1774.5
  },
  {
    "text": "Now that's weird.",
    "start": 1776.83,
    "end": 1777.70999
  },
  {
    "text": "Right?",
    "start": 1777.70999,
    "end": 1777.87
  },
  {
    "text": "Here we have two people who like Jesus.",
    "start": 1779.71,
    "end": 1783.34999
  },
  {
    "text": "They're pro Jesus.",
    "start": 1784.57,
    "end": 1786.49
  },
  {
    "text": "In fact,",
    "start": 1786.49,
    "end": 1786.73
  },
  {
    "text": "one of him one of them calls him teacher,",
    "start": 1786.87,
    "end": 1788.79
  },
  {
    "text": "and the other calls him lord.",
    "start": 1788.79,
    "end": 1789.91
  },
  {
    "text": "Both want to follow Jesus,",
    "start": 1790.65002,
    "end": 1792.25
  },
  {
    "text": "and yet, weirdly, Jesus seems to try and turn them away.",
    "start": 1793.02,
    "end": 1796.06
  },
  {
    "text": "Or at least what he does",
    "start": 1798.34998,
    "end": 1799.38998
  },
  {
    "text": "is he challenges their expectations of what it means to truly follow him.",
    "start": 1800.28,
    "end": 1805.50998
  },
  {
    "text": "By lifting up the bar,",
    "start": 1807.19,
    "end": 1808.3899999999999
  },
  {
    "text": "by raising it up,",
    "start": 1809.27,
    "end": 1810.38998
  },
  {
    "text": "in two ways,",
    "start": 1811.65,
    "end": 1812.93
  },
  {
    "text": "really.",
    "start": 1812.93,
    "end": 1813.25
  },
  {
    "text": "First, with regards to comfort.",
    "start": 1813.25,
    "end": 1814.83
  },
  {
    "text": "He says the son of man has no place to rest his head.",
    "start": 1814.83,
    "end": 1817.31
  },
  {
    "text": "He's got no home.",
    "start": 1817.31,
    "end": 1818.03
  },
  {
    "text": "Jesus is saying here the journey,",
    "start": 1818.59,
    "end": 1820.27
  },
  {
    "text": "if you follow me,",
    "start": 1820.27,
    "end": 1820.99
  },
  {
    "text": "it's uncomfortable.",
    "start": 1820.99,
    "end": 1821.79
  },
  {
    "text": "Yeah.",
    "start": 1821.79,
    "end": 1821.87
  },
  {
    "text": "Won't be easy.",
    "start": 1822.29,
    "end": 1823.01
  },
  {
    "text": "And you have to be prepared to be uncomfortable at times too.",
    "start": 1824.4,
    "end": 1827.3600000000001
  },
  {
    "text": "And in the second way,",
    "start": 1828.75,
    "end": 1829.71
  },
  {
    "text": "he he challenges his priorities.",
    "start": 1829.71,
    "end": 1831.93002
  },
  {
    "text": "What's first in his life?",
    "start": 1831.93002,
    "end": 1833.45
  },
  {
    "text": "Did you notice that there?",
    "start": 1833.45,
    "end": 1834.25
  },
  {
    "text": "The second disciple says,",
    "start": 1834.40997,
    "end": 1835.77
  },
  {
    "text": "yeah.",
    "start": 1835.77,
    "end": 1836.00998
  },
  {
    "text": "Yeah.",
    "start": 1836.00998,
    "end": 1836.1699800000001
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm keen to follow you,",
    "start": 1836.1699800000001,
    "end": 1836.97
  },
  {
    "text": "Jesus,",
    "start": 1836.97,
    "end": 1837.28998
  },
  {
    "text": "but first, let me and Jesus says,",
    "start": 1837.28998,
    "end": 1839.21
  },
  {
    "text": "no.",
    "start": 1839.21,
    "end": 1839.29
  },
  {
    "text": "No.",
    "start": 1839.29,
    "end": 1839.6100000000001
  },
  {
    "text": "No.",
    "start": 1839.6100000000001,
    "end": 1839.69
  },
  {
    "text": "No.",
    "start": 1839.69,
    "end": 1839.85
  },
  {
    "text": "No.",
    "start": 1839.85,
    "end": 1839.93
  },
  {
    "text": "Me first.",
    "start": 1841.61002,
    "end": 1842.25
  },
  {
    "text": "Me before everything,",
    "start": 1843.69,
    "end": 1845.05
  },
  {
    "text": "even good things.",
    "start": 1845.05,
    "end": 1845.77
  },
  {
    "text": "Even really good things like your family,",
    "start": 1847.1999799999999,
    "end": 1849.04
  },
  {
    "text": "like burying your dead dad.",
    "start": 1849.04,
    "end": 1850.08
  },
  {
    "text": "And you read that right,",
    "start": 1852.18002,
    "end": 1853.38
  },
  {
    "text": "and you think,",
    "start": 1853.38,
    "end": 1853.86002
  },
  {
    "text": "well, you know, like, yes, but this and this and and also,",
    "start": 1853.86002,
    "end": 1857.87997
  },
  {
    "text": "you know, dude,",
    "start": 1857.87997,
    "end": 1858.28
  },
  {
    "text": "family's important and all,",
    "start": 1858.28,
    "end": 1859.47998
  },
  {
    "text": "but you think,",
    "start": 1859.47998,
    "end": 1860.22
  },
  {
    "text": "well, you know, just calm down a little bit here,",
    "start": 1860.22,
    "end": 1862.54
  },
  {
    "text": "Jesus.",
    "start": 1862.54,
    "end": 1862.86002
  },
  {
    "text": "Isn't this a little bit extreme?",
    "start": 1862.86002,
    "end": 1863.82
  },
  {
    "text": "Isn't this a little bit unbalanced?",
    "start": 1864.93,
    "end": 1866.53
  },
  {
    "text": "And you know what it is?",
    "start": 1867.93,
    "end": 1869.13
  },
  {
    "text": "That's precisely the point.",
    "start": 1871.1,
    "end": 1872.78
  },
  {
    "text": "There's no balanced life",
    "start": 1875.57,
    "end": 1877.01
  },
  {
    "text": "when you follow Jesus.",
    "start": 1877.69,
    "end": 1878.88998
  },
  {
    "text": "And it's not enough to like him",
    "start": 1880.3000200000001,
    "end": 1881.82
  },
  {
    "text": "It's not enough to be pro him.",
    "start": 1883.0,
    "end": 1884.84
  },
  {
    "text": "It's not even enough to give him a lot of your life,",
    "start": 1885.88998,
    "end": 1888.53
  },
  {
    "text": "parts of most of it.",
    "start": 1888.53,
    "end": 1889.73
  },
  {
    "text": "Right?",
    "start": 1889.73,
    "end": 1889.88998
  },
  {
    "text": "You gotta go all in.",
    "start": 1891.71,
    "end": 1892.91
  },
  {
    "text": "He doesn't want your lip service.",
    "start": 1895.06998,
    "end": 1896.6699800000001
  },
  {
    "text": "He wants your heart",
    "start": 1898.18,
    "end": 1899.46
  },
  {
    "text": "He wants your devotion.",
    "start": 1901.25,
    "end": 1902.53003
  },
  {
    "text": "Your focus,",
    "start": 1903.13,
    "end": 1904.41
  },
  {
    "text": "your love.",
    "start": 1904.49,
    "end": 1905.29
  },
  {
    "text": "He wants your whole life.",
    "start": 1905.29,
    "end": 1906.57
  },
  {
    "text": "That's what it means to follow Jesus.",
    "start": 1909.03,
    "end": 1910.9499799999999
  },
  {
    "text": "That's what his power and his goodness demand.",
    "start": 1912.82,
    "end": 1915.1399999999999
  },
  {
    "text": "All in,",
    "start": 1917.86002,
    "end": 1918.42
  },
  {
    "text": "with everything.",
    "start": 1919.68,
    "end": 1920.4
  },
  {
    "text": "Such that the entirety of your life is pushed through that litmus test",
    "start": 1924.06,
    "end": 1930.22
  },
  {
    "text": "that that lens of how is this about Jesus?",
    "start": 1930.22,
    "end": 1932.92
  },
  {
    "text": "How is this decision about Jesus?",
    "start": 1934.24,
    "end": 1936.08
  },
  {
    "text": "How does this love Jesus?",
    "start": 1937.28,
    "end": 1939.12
  },
  {
    "text": "How how is how is what I'm doing,",
    "start": 1939.12,
    "end": 1940.86002
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm thinking,",
    "start": 1940.86002,
    "end": 1941.18002
  },
  {
    "text": "and I'm feeling?",
    "start": 1941.18002,
    "end": 1942.06003
  },
  {
    "text": "How does this honor and glorify and magnify Jesus?",
    "start": 1942.06003,
    "end": 1945.53
  },
  {
    "text": "And Jesus says,",
    "start": 1945.53,
    "end": 1946.76
  },
  {
    "text": "yeah.",
    "start": 1946.76,
    "end": 1946.92
  },
  {
    "text": "This is it.",
    "start": 1946.92,
    "end": 1947.96
  },
  {
    "text": "Do this,",
    "start": 1947.96,
    "end": 1948.44
  },
  {
    "text": "and I'll take you through some hard places.",
    "start": 1948.44,
    "end": 1950.36002
  },
  {
    "text": "Yeah.",
    "start": 1950.36002,
    "end": 1950.52002
  },
  {
    "text": "Gonna cost you.",
    "start": 1952.31,
    "end": 1953.1100000000001
  },
  {
    "text": "At times,",
    "start": 1954.29,
    "end": 1954.93
  },
  {
    "text": "it's gonna be uncomfortable.",
    "start": 1954.93,
    "end": 1956.45
  },
  {
    "text": "High bar.",
    "start": 1956.53,
    "end": 1957.25
  },
  {
    "text": "But don't you know me?",
    "start": 1959.22,
    "end": 1960.5
  },
  {
    "text": "Don't you know my power?",
    "start": 1962.62,
    "end": 1964.06
  },
  {
    "text": "Don't you know my goodness?",
    "start": 1965.91,
    "end": 1967.75
  },
  {
    "text": "Don't you know I've got you?",
    "start": 1968.6,
    "end": 1969.96
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm with you.",
    "start": 1969.96,
    "end": 1970.68
  },
  {
    "text": "Come on.",
    "start": 1970.68,
    "end": 1971.0
  },
  {
    "text": "Get in.",
    "start": 1972.02002,
    "end": 1972.5800199999999
  },
  {
    "text": "My favorite verse in this whole passage is kind of a weird verse.",
    "start": 1975.53998,
    "end": 1980.05
  },
  {
    "text": "It's it's chapter eight verse twenty three.",
    "start": 1980.05,
    "end": 1981.56998
  },
  {
    "text": "Initially, it does doesn't seem like much.",
    "start": 1982.4199800000001,
    "end": 1984.34
  },
  {
    "text": "It doesn't seem that important.",
    "start": 1984.34,
    "end": 1985.21997
  },
  {
    "text": "But when you understand the context of what Jesus has just said,",
    "start": 1985.62,
    "end": 1988.5
  },
  {
    "text": "it is absolutely awesome,",
    "start": 1989.2,
    "end": 1991.13
  },
  {
    "text": "and it's so encouraging.",
    "start": 1991.13,
    "end": 1992.25
  },
  {
    "text": "Jesus lays down the gauntlet.",
    "start": 1993.87,
    "end": 1995.71
  },
  {
    "text": "He says,",
    "start": 1995.71,
    "end": 1996.03
  },
  {
    "text": "all in everything.",
    "start": 1996.53,
    "end": 1997.57
  },
  {
    "text": "That's what it means to follow me.",
    "start": 1997.57,
    "end": 1998.93002
  },
  {
    "text": "And then look at what happens there in verse twenty three.",
    "start": 1998.93002,
    "end": 2001.17
  },
  {
    "text": "Then he got into the boat,",
    "start": 2003.18002,
    "end": 2004.38
  },
  {
    "text": "and his disciples,",
    "start": 2004.71,
    "end": 2006.06998
  },
  {
    "text": "what?",
    "start": 2006.06998,
    "end": 2006.38998
  },
  {
    "text": "His followed him.",
    "start": 2007.98,
    "end": 2010.50998
  },
  {
    "text": "Into the storm.",
    "start": 2012.21,
    "end": 2013.09
  },
  {
    "text": "Past the demon possessed man,",
    "start": 2014.57,
    "end": 2016.01
  },
  {
    "text": "beyond the paralyzed guy all the way to the cross.",
    "start": 2017.6,
    "end": 2021.85
  },
  {
    "text": "And then they gave their whole lives to him,",
    "start": 2023.49002,
    "end": 2025.57
  },
  {
    "text": "In fact,",
    "start": 2026.35,
    "end": 2026.99
  },
  {
    "text": "they gave up their lives for him.",
    "start": 2026.99,
    "end": 2028.51
  },
  {
    "text": "And they weren't perfect,",
    "start": 2030.16,
    "end": 2031.52
  },
  {
    "text": "there times,",
    "start": 2031.52,
    "end": 2032.0
  },
  {
    "text": "stuffed it up.",
    "start": 2032.22,
    "end": 2032.94
  },
  {
    "text": "We all do,",
    "start": 2032.94,
    "end": 2033.5
  },
  {
    "text": "of course,",
    "start": 2033.5,
    "end": 2034.06
  },
  {
    "text": "but here's the thing.",
    "start": 2034.06,
    "end": 2035.02
  },
  {
    "text": "They got in the boat with Jesus.",
    "start": 2037.11002,
    "end": 2039.11002
  },
  {
    "text": "All in everything.",
    "start": 2040.58,
    "end": 2041.38
  },
  {
    "text": "So tell me,",
    "start": 2045.65,
    "end": 2046.53
  },
  {
    "text": "are you in the boat Jesus this morning?",
    "start": 2048.20996,
    "end": 2050.8
  },
  {
    "text": "Or are you just watching from a distance?",
    "start": 2053.41003,
    "end": 2055.01
  },
  {
    "text": "From the shore?",
    "start": 2056.2799999999997,
    "end": 2057.16003
  },
  {
    "text": "Not yet committing to Jesus,",
    "start": 2058.86,
    "end": 2060.3
  },
  {
    "text": "holding him at arm's length,",
    "start": 2060.3,
    "end": 2062.44
  },
  {
    "text": "perhaps it is that you find yourself half in the boat.",
    "start": 2062.86,
    "end": 2065.5
  },
  {
    "text": "One foot on the boat,",
    "start": 2066.36,
    "end": 2067.3999599999997
  },
  {
    "text": "one foot on the shore,",
    "start": 2067.3999599999997,
    "end": 2068.27997
  },
  {
    "text": "honoring Jesus with your lips,",
    "start": 2068.76,
    "end": 2070.2799999999997
  },
  {
    "text": "by keeping something back?",
    "start": 2071.16003,
    "end": 2072.52
  },
  {
    "text": "Of your life,",
    "start": 2073.2,
    "end": 2074.08
  },
  {
    "text": "of your love,",
    "start": 2074.08,
    "end": 2074.8
  },
  {
    "text": "of your devotion to him.",
    "start": 2074.8,
    "end": 2075.83997
  },
  {
    "text": "Personally, this is my biggest fear.",
    "start": 2078.1100500000002,
    "end": 2080.59
  },
  {
    "text": "That I'll settle in for Luke warm middle class comfortable Christianity.",
    "start": 2082.52,
    "end": 2086.77
  },
  {
    "text": "That my love and and and my devotion for him just with little compromise after little compromise will eventually grow cold.",
    "start": 2087.67,
    "end": 2096.08997
  },
  {
    "text": "And I'm worried that one day,",
    "start": 2096.08997,
    "end": 2097.85
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm gonna wake up",
    "start": 2097.85,
    "end": 2098.57
  },
  {
    "text": "and Jesus and the boat will be all the way over there.",
    "start": 2099.27,
    "end": 2102.44
  },
  {
    "text": "And I'm I'm back here,",
    "start": 2103.87,
    "end": 2105.70996
  },
  {
    "text": "and I think,",
    "start": 2105.70996,
    "end": 2106.19
  },
  {
    "text": "what happened?",
    "start": 2106.19,
    "end": 2106.51
  },
  {
    "text": "I don't wanna be that purse",
    "start": 2108.74,
    "end": 2110.02
  },
  {
    "text": "I pray it won't be I pray it won't be you either.",
    "start": 2111.58997,
    "end": 2114.74
  },
  {
    "text": "Is that who you wanna be?",
    "start": 2114.74,
    "end": 2115.7
  },
  {
    "text": "You know, the one thing that's gonna keep that from happening",
    "start": 2118.49,
    "end": 2121.19
  },
  {
    "text": "is remembering Jesus' power and his goodness.",
    "start": 2123.04,
    "end": 2126.37
  },
  {
    "text": "Every day.",
    "start": 2127.31,
    "end": 2127.95
  },
  {
    "text": "Every moment,",
    "start": 2128.81,
    "end": 2129.69
  },
  {
    "text": "from here until he returns,",
    "start": 2130.34,
    "end": 2131.94
  },
  {
    "text": "continuing to say,",
    "start": 2132.74,
    "end": 2133.8600500000002
  },
  {
    "text": "yes, Jesus.",
    "start": 2133.8600500000002,
    "end": 2134.5
  },
  {
    "text": "I'll follow you all in everything on the boat,",
    "start": 2134.5,
    "end": 2137.47003
  },
  {
    "text": "Here we go.",
    "start": 2137.61,
    "end": 2138.17
  },
  {
    "text": "So here's what I wanna do as we we wrap up now.",
    "start": 2140.83997,
    "end": 2143.32
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm gonna invite the the band to come up",
    "start": 2144.15,
    "end": 2146.15
  },
  {
    "text": "and and they're gonna lead us in song in a moment",
    "start": 2146.92,
    "end": 2149.8
  },
  {
    "text": "But as they do that,",
    "start": 2150.09,
    "end": 2151.05005
  },
  {
    "text": "I just want you to take a moment",
    "start": 2152.0,
    "end": 2153.36
  },
  {
    "text": "to stop and to think about your life.",
    "start": 2153.36,
    "end": 2156.55005
  },
  {
    "text": "And think about your loves and",
    "start": 2157.8,
    "end": 2161.23
  },
  {
    "text": "where it is you're at with Jesus this morning.",
    "start": 2161.23,
    "end": 2163.07
  },
  {
    "text": "What at this point might might you be holding back",
    "start": 2165.05,
    "end": 2168.85
  },
  {
    "text": "and what is one step you could take to do something about it?",
    "start": 2169.39,
    "end": 2172.59
  },
  {
    "text": "Maybe there's something you wanna start doing this week,",
    "start": 2174.23,
    "end": 2176.63
  },
  {
    "text": "this afternoon,",
    "start": 2176.63,
    "end": 2177.11
  },
  {
    "text": "Maybe there's someone you wanna talk to.",
    "start": 2178.91003,
    "end": 2181.30005
  },
  {
    "text": "You wanna ask for help with that.",
    "start": 2181.30005,
    "end": 2182.5
  },
  {
    "text": "Maybe write it down.",
    "start": 2184.24,
    "end": 2185.19995
  },
  {
    "text": "On your phone.",
    "start": 2185.68,
    "end": 2186.72003
  },
  {
    "text": "Text it to someone.",
    "start": 2186.72003,
    "end": 2187.76
  },
  {
    "text": "Get some accountability and support.",
    "start": 2187.76,
    "end": 2189.3600500000002
  },
  {
    "text": "That can be so helpful,",
    "start": 2189.3600500000002,
    "end": 2191.0299999999997
  },
  {
    "text": "can't it?",
    "start": 2191.0299999999997,
    "end": 2191.3500400000003
  },
  {
    "text": "Just take a moment",
    "start": 2192.35,
    "end": 2193.23
  },
  {
    "text": "to think about whether you're on the boat",
    "start": 2193.23,
    "end": 2195.99
  },
  {
    "text": "and what you're holding back",
    "start": 2197.18,
    "end": 2198.46
  },
  {
    "text": "and then I'm gonna lead us in prayer",
    "start": 2199.85,
    "end": 2201.52997
  },
  {
    "text": "before we sing together.",
    "start": 2202.2,
    "end": 2203.32
  },
  {
    "text": "I'll give you a little moment to do that.",
    "start": 2203.32,
    "end": 2204.44
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's pray.",
    "start": 2206.29,
    "end": 2206.93
  },
  {
    "text": "Heavenly father,",
    "start": 2209.38,
    "end": 2210.26
  },
  {
    "text": "we thank you for Jesus.",
    "start": 2211.38,
    "end": 2212.8999599999997
  },
  {
    "text": "For his power,",
    "start": 2214.27,
    "end": 2215.23
  },
  {
    "text": "for his goodness,",
    "start": 2216.1000400000003,
    "end": 2217.14
  },
  {
    "text": "And we pray that you would help us to fear him",
    "start": 2218.75,
    "end": 2221.65
  },
  {
    "text": "but not just fear him to trust him.",
    "start": 2222.44,
    "end": 2224.2
  },
  {
    "text": "To put our faith in him.",
    "start": 2225.4700000000003,
    "end": 2226.91
  },
  {
    "text": "Father,",
    "start": 2228.9,
    "end": 2229.3
  },
  {
    "text": "we ask that you would help us to put our faith in the reality",
    "start": 2229.3,
    "end": 2233.14
  },
  {
    "text": "and the truth that he'll use his power for our good.",
    "start": 2233.14,
    "end": 2236.1000400000003
  },
  {
    "text": "Because he's good.",
    "start": 2237.86,
    "end": 2239.35
  },
  {
    "text": "And we pray this",
    "start": 2241.26,
    "end": 2242.14
  },
  {
    "text": "especially when we don't feel that in our lives,",
    "start": 2242.14,
    "end": 2244.79
  },
  {
    "text": "when that's not our day to day experience,",
    "start": 2244.79,
    "end": 2246.4700000000003
  },
  {
    "text": "We pray you'll hand us in",
    "start": 2247.13,
    "end": 2248.33
  },
  {
    "text": "and you'll hold us by bringing us back to the cross.",
    "start": 2248.33,
    "end": 2252.33997
  },
  {
    "text": "To Jesus' death",
    "start": 2253.55,
    "end": 2254.51
  },
  {
    "text": "in the empty tomb.",
    "start": 2254.51,
    "end": 2255.39
  },
  {
    "text": "To the sure promise of forgiveness and the steadfast hope of eternal life.",
    "start": 2257.1000400000003,
    "end": 2262.62006
  },
  {
    "text": "And that day when he comes and makes all things new.",
    "start": 2263.92,
    "end": 2266.6399499999998
  },
  {
    "text": "So, father,",
    "start": 2268.93,
    "end": 2269.6499599999997
  },
  {
    "text": "please help us to follow him.",
    "start": 2269.6499599999997,
    "end": 2272.04004
  },
  {
    "text": "All in,",
    "start": 2272.9700000000003,
    "end": 2273.69
  },
  {
    "text": "Everything.",
    "start": 2274.18,
    "end": 2274.58
  },
  {
    "text": "Help us to get on the boat.",
    "start": 2275.6499599999997,
    "end": 2277.25
  },
  {
    "text": "And we pray particularly",
    "start": 2278.92,
    "end": 2280.19995
  },
  {
    "text": "that you would forgive us,",
    "start": 2280.19995,
    "end": 2281.79
  },
  {
    "text": "father,",
    "start": 2281.79,
    "end": 2282.11
  },
  {
    "text": "that we're often so lukewarm in this.",
    "start": 2282.11,
    "end": 2284.43
  },
  {
    "text": "We acknowledge and we confess to you our shortcomings and our failings.",
    "start": 2285.73,
    "end": 2289.25
  },
  {
    "text": "But, father,",
    "start": 2291.14,
    "end": 2291.7
  },
  {
    "text": "we thank you",
    "start": 2291.7,
    "end": 2292.18
  },
  {
    "text": "that even still you love us,",
    "start": 2292.18,
    "end": 2293.62
  },
  {
    "text": "and you lead us",
    "start": 2294.31,
    "end": 2295.35
  },
  {
    "text": "and you guide us",
    "start": 2296.09,
    "end": 2297.21
  },
  {
    "text": "We do love you,",
    "start": 2298.54004,
    "end": 2300.14
  },
  {
    "text": "father.",
    "start": 2300.14,
    "end": 2300.3
  },
  {
    "text": "And we do love Jesus,",
    "start": 2300.6,
    "end": 2301.88
  },
  {
    "text": "and we ask that you would help us to love him more and more.",
    "start": 2301.88,
    "end": 2304.27997
  },
  {
    "text": "In Jesus' name,",
    "start": 2305.39,
    "end": 2306.27
  },
  {
    "text": "we pray.",
    "start": 2306.27,
    "end": 2306.59
  },
  {
    "text": "Amen.",
    "start": 2307.08997,
    "end": 2307.49
  }
]